BACKEND REMOTE STATE MANAGEMENT


THROUGH GRAPHICAL MODE IN  GCS CREATE THE STORAGE BUCKET


terraform {
  backend "gcs" {
    bucket = "bucket1witheng"   # same name you created above
    prefix = "terraform/state"
    credentials = "terra.json"
                            
  }
}


